en.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%C3%A2n-Phong-chi%E1%BA%BFt-t%C3%BD-%C3%B4ng/poem-KtBm_SbkVga0HsQGBtpOwA">Tân Phong chiết tý ông - 新豐折臂翁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/T%E1%BB%B1-Thi%C3%AAn-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ph%E1%BB%A7-phi%C3%AAu-qu%C3%A1-h%E1%BA%A3i-kh%E1%BA%A9u-ng%E1%BB%99-phong/poem-0iV8AiGJXV87Q6IYw8o8Aw">Tự Thiên Trường phủ phiêu quá hải khẩu ngộ phong - 自天長府漂過海口遇風</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4-S%E1%BB%9F-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-ki%C3%AAm-m%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-VusrYuqrkvq24lkjJ2HUYQ">Tương thích Ngô Sở, lưu biệt Chương sứ quân lưu hậu kiêm mạc phủ chư công, đắc liễu tự - 將適吳楚，留別章使君留後兼幕府諸公，得柳字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Giang-Nam/poem-sIF1dXuMLGcAaa7Y0nrIIQ">Vọng Giang Nam - 望江南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
